			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Electrodeionization involves a continuous process of electrochemical water deionization using ion-specific membranes, mixed-bed resins and a direct current voltage. It is safer than classical treatments with acids, bases and other chemicals. It produces highly pure water, allows efficient ion removal and is an effective technological solution for removing unwanted ions from your water supply. It is also referred to as Continuous Electrodeionization (CEDI) and Continuous Deionization (CDI).</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">电去离子是利用离子特异性膜、混合床树脂和直流电压对水进行电化学去离子的连续过程。与传统的使用酸、碱和其他化学品的处理方法相比，电去离子法更为安全。它能产生高纯水，有效去除离子，是去除供水中不需要的离子的有效技术解决方案。它也被称为连续电去离子（CEDI）和连续去离子（CDI）。</common:generalComment>
